Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,where they instigated an all-out war against the New Fishman Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,who were holding a grudge against humans and looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy finally defeated Hody, the captain of the New Fishman Pirates, in a fierce fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and thwarted his plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,2 years ago at a Sky Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I read a Poneglyph indicating where one of the ancient weapons is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mermaid Princess who lived around the same time as Joyboy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...was known by a specific name, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...Poseidon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:22.75,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Straw Hats Stunned! The New Fleet Admiral of the Navy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know their purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but a long time ago, there were powerful entities that could destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They were 3 Ancient Weapons given the names of gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pluton, Uranus, and Poseidon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.85,0:05:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let anyone know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Every powerful group in the world would want Princess Shirahoshi's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The Government--even pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ancient Weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They could destroy the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got all their treasure and I was about to leave
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.48,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is even bigger news!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So that Mermaid Princess is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew, I want seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You already ate it all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good--I could eat this forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially this candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as good as meat. I want hundreds of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm afraid we are running out of that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We can bring other things if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about the state of the world now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you asking all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you know nothing. You're out of the loop--that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.25,0:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a light snack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you guys are here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I drank too much! I'm trying to sober up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji Mermaid-ed too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.18,0:07:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like heaven! The Mermaid Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Red Hound and Blue Pheasant had a big fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't even know about that, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear about anything during my training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew about it! I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after the war 2 years ago, Fleet Admiral Sengoku resigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sengoku recommended Blue Pheasant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to be his successor since he was very popular among his own men
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but a lot of people at the highest level favored Red Hound
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and so he became a major contender.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.20,0:08:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, Blue Pheasant doesn't show his passion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but he hated the idea of Red Hound becoming a Fleet Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They stood against each other and the first-ever feud between the Admirals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...erupted into a battle on an island somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the saying "Dead men tell no tales,"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,whoever lost had to withdraw his candidacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The winner would lead the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As all the world now knows, their deadly struggle lasted for 10 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were comparable in their strength but it came to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Hound won!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakazuki is the new Fleet Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Blue Pheasant die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They were both severely wounded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and though Red Hound is pitiless, he showed mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to his former comrade who couldn't even stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Blue Pheasant refused to work for Red Hound
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so he left the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a Navy soldier now, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.01,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he is not. I wonder where he is and what he is thinking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a big loss for the Government, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. The Admirals were the Navy's greatest powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But what the Government did to cover their loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...gave the Navy unexpected power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. You all need to know the two biggest changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...which have occurred in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First, Navy Headquarters led by Sakazuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...has become an even more powerful force for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And second,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the Blackbeard Pirates have advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We met them in Mock Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They destroyed my hometown once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The new era they're talking about is crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The era where pirates have dreams will be over, they say?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.42,0:10:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,People's dreams... have no end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I never gave you my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He was once a long-time member of the Whitebeard Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows their territory very well
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and he conquered it in an instant after the old chap died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the Tremor-Tremor Fruit power that he got from the old chap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The world already counts him among...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...Red-Haired, Kaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and considers him as one of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So he took Whitebeard's place successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dirty rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that they are on the hunt for Devil Fruit users.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They can somehow acquire a Devil Fruit user's power after killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.60,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep looking for stronger Devil Fruit powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants your Human-Human Fruit power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.11,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you, Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a lot of bad blood between you and Blackbeard--Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So take extra care...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Are you even listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to know a little bit of information at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We were listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought captains normally don't listen to other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.38,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Captains are responsible for their crew's safety, aren't they, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Jinbe, take it easy! I like taking chances anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be hard to work for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here. You're the life of the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Wimpyhoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess-sama said she's tired and she wanted to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so she went to her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there is a wild animal or something in this palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.44,OS,,0,0,0,,THE HARD SHELL TOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not know it's such fun to party with everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so resentful, Princess-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'm not gonna hurt you or make you suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was content with taking the treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.21,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It became a pain to sell those Mermaids
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're an exception!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need you to be unconscious for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got word from my brother and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they've arrived at a port on this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the New World with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Why don't you laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyah, nyah, nyah, nyah, nyah, boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Straw Hat? I'm having fun here so go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyah, nyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyah, nyah, nyah! Nyah, nyah, nyah... Nya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know he was still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so lucky, Luffy! I should have kicked him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the pirate that we captured in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him since we entered Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close! Thank you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the treasure thief was still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:17:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We usually don't even let a tiny fish into the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but the gate was left open in the confusion of the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! That tower on the right has been sliced clean through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I assume the thief did it while we were not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this guy cut the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,When they escaped from the cage, he cut bars, walls... everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to tell him that, you stupid starfish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! As they say, lying and stealing are next-door neighbors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, Minister of the Right-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.63,0:17:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say "treasure thief"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he stole all the treasures in the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! He did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they national treasures? You're not gonna go after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing my people's lives be saved, treasures mean nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're worth something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we get them back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You can keep them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be wonderful if people who saved the country had them-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools! Why did you kick him out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you just punch him and tie him up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it even when you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go find him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,K-King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong with Hody and the others! Their cuffs came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:31.69,OS,,0,0,0,,THE PRISON TOWER
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn humans! Our grudge against you will never go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.23,0:18:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our time to avenge will come again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Straw Hat here! I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.36,0:19:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel pain in my joints!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I got old on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get back at the Straw Hats-fosun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the ones who will punish humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Hody and his clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that you can keep me in jail, you stupid royal family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-These bars are nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! The Energy Steroid that you guys were taking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.51,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...was the legendary pill that was kept in the Tamate Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamate Box?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was national treasure that had been passed down for generations-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,10 years ago, somebody stole the contents of the Tamate Box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find who did it and by the King's decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,we closed the case before it became a scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that was when you left the army, Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The legendary pill had unclear effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One explanation says it gives you tremendous power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Another explanation says it just makes you old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an odd national treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed they guarded the power drug closely
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to seal off its dangerous effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You folk opened the box that should not be opened
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and dreamed a foolish dream of gaining some power-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like they no longer get their revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We're chosen avengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We will kill all humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will consider giving them clemency.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Neptune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukaboshi, you're a dishonor to our race!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Island will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:22:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed my mother but I will not hold a grudge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So please. Just shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want the children on the island to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pekoms and Baron Tamago arrived at the Candy Factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.63,0:22:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They were sent by Big Mom. This is not a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are our sweets? Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama is waiting for them-soir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any sweets to pay them for this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody and the others destroyed the factory
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:22:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and the undamaged sweets have
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:22:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,been sent to the banquet since everybody wanted the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.33,0:23:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hats to have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we can explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She is like a monster who would destroy a whole country for sweets!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Four Emperors...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and the others are caught up trying to reclaim the treasure of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The crew of Big Mom, one of the Four Emperors, shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Fishman Island faces destruction yet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the hands of one of the overwhelmingly powerful Four Emperors...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...Luffy takes a stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.63,0:23:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.30,0:23:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"She Loves Sweets! Big Mom of the Four Emperors!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
